With partner [[Carissa Guild]], he is the 1996 [[U.S. Figure Skating Championships|U.S. novice silver medalist]]. They won the bronze medal at the [[1997-1998 ISU Junior Series]] event in Slovakia and placed 12th at the [[1997 World Junior Figure Skating Championships]]. [http://www.iceskatingintnl.com/archive/results/jrwrld97.htm 1997 World Junior Figure Skating Championships] Muldoon also competed with partners [[Naomi Grabow]] and [[Ingrid Goldberg]]{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}. He skated professionally in [[Disney on Ice]]{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}, [[Radio City Music Hall]]'s Christmas Spectacular{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}, and Cold Rhythm{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}. Andrew Muldoon is a graduate of [[Edinboro University of Pennsylvania]]{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}. ==Results== Pairs (with Guild) {| class="wikitable" |- !
